<view class="jl-page {{__themeDark ? 'dark-theme' : ''}} secondary-shell" style="padding-top: {{navSafeTop}}px;"><view class="secondary-nav secondary-nav--back-only"><view class="secondary-nav__back" bindtap="goBack" data-secondary-route="packages/java-course/pages/lesson/lesson"><text class="secondary-nav__back-icon">‹</text></view></view><block wx:if="{{loadError}}"><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-empty-title">小节暂不可用</text><text class="jl-copy">找不到这个 Java 小节。请返回章节目录重新进入。</text><view class="jl-btn" bindtap="goBack">返回</view></view></block><block wx:else><view class="jl-head"><text class="jl-kicker">Java Lesson</text><text class="jl-title">{{lesson.title.ja}}</text><text class="jl-sub">{{lesson.title.zh}}</text><text class="jl-source">{{lesson.sourceRef.chapter}} · {{lesson.sourceRef.pageStart}} 页</text></view><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-card-title">この節で学ぶこと / 本节你将学会什么</text><view wx:for="{{lesson.objectives}}" wx:key="ja"><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.zh}}</text></view></view><view class="jl-card" wx:for="{{lesson.prerequisites}}" wx:key="ja"><text class="jl-card-title">零基础前置说明</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.zh}}</text></view><view class="jl-card" wx:for="{{lesson.blocks}}" wx:key="semanticKey"><text class="jl-card-title">{{item.title.ja}}</text><text class="jl-card-sub">{{item.title.zh}}</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.zh}}</text></view><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-card-title">核心术语</text><view class="jl-term" wx:for="{{lesson.terms}}" wx:key="en"><text class="jl-term__name">{{item.ja}} / {{item.zh}} / {{item.en}}</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.explanationJa}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.explanationZh}}</text></view></view><view class="jl-card" wx:for="{{lesson.codeExamples}}" wx:key="exampleId" wx:for-index="codeIndex"><view class="jl-code-head"><text class="jl-card-title">Java</text><view class="jl-copy-btn" bindtap="copyCode" data-index="{{codeIndex}}">复制</view></view><scroll-view scroll-x="true" class="java-code-scroll"><text class="java-code">{{item.code}}</text></scroll-view><text class="jl-card-sub">预期输出</text><text class="java-output">{{item.expectedOutput}}</text><view wx:for="{{item.lineNotes}}" wx:key="ja"><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.zh}}</text></view></view><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-card-title">常见错误</text><view wx:for="{{lesson.commonMistakes}}" wx:key="ja"><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{item.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{item.zh}}</text></view></view><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-card-title">小结</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{lesson.summary.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{lesson.summary.zh}}</text></view><view class="jl-card"><text class="jl-card-title">下一节的关系</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{lesson.nextLessonBridge.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{lesson.nextLessonBridge.zh}}</text></view><view class="jl-card jl-card--handson"><text class="jl-card-title">手を動かしてみよう / 动手试试看</text><text class="jl-copy jl-copy--ja">{{lesson.handson.ja}}</text><text class="jl-copy">{{lesson.handson.zh}}</text></view></block></view>
